From 7410291f8ecfbaa50c7b042753abe4efd5c80f70 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jerad Shoemaker <jshoemakerhwc@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 09:04:18 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Fix blog CSS loading on netlify.app domain and add Edge
 compatibility

Change Hugo template asset links from absURL to relURL so CSS/favicons
load correctly when site is accessed via psychopharmref.netlify.app
(e.g. behind corporate proxies that block the custom domain). Add
X-UA-Compatible meta tag across all pages and Netlify headers for
Microsoft Edge compatibility.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
